@Ocelot93 Shinji isn't developing it, and he didn't develop Shadows either.  He provided resources.  Suda only provided some character concepts and I'm pretty sure he wrote those story books.  Everything else, he left to his crew.
Lolipop seems to have even less involvement with him providing character concepts and bringing a Hollywood writer and letting other people do it.
I like it so much better when he was more involved.  Like in Killer7 for example.  He wrote that, fully involved.
